705809f-c.title: Brooklyn: Myrtle Avenue - Portland Avenue (North)
705809f-c.text:
Myrtle Avenue (El,thereon), west from North Portland Avenue to Leo Place, showing extensive demolition for the erection of Nort Lreene Houses. The view is from 'ort Greene Park. In the background is St. Edwards Roman Gatholic Ghurch.
View 2 is across the same area, from Ashland Plece. View 3 is south from North Portland and Park Svenues toward Myrtle Avenue.
P. L. Snerr  April 11, 1941
NO RRPRODDCTIONS  Views 1-3
